## Proposed Changes

### [District Context & Routing]

#### [MODIFY] [DistrictContext.jsx](file:///C:/Users/soren/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/mess-khojo/client/src/context/DistrictContext.jsx)
- **URL Parameter Detection**: Initialize `selectedDistrict` state by checking `URLSearchParams` first:
  ```javascript
  const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
  const districtParam = params.get('district')?.toLowerCase();
  if (districtParam && DISTRICTS_CONFIG[districtParam]?.active) {
      localStorage.setItem('selectedDistrict', districtParam);
      return districtParam;
  }
  ```
- **Syncing URL on Selection**: Update `setSelectedDistrict` function to sync the URL parameter using `window.history.replaceState` when a district is selected or reset:
  ```javascript
  const url = new URL(window.location.href);
  if (districtId) {
      url.searchParams.set('district', districtId);
  } else {
      url.searchParams.delete('district');
  }
  window.history.replaceState({}, '', url.toString());
  ```

